## 2. Description of Service

Printify Automation is a Chrome browser extension that helps users create products on Printify more efficiently through automation and AI-powered content generation. The Service includes:

- Bulk product creation tools
- AI-generated titles and descriptions
- Multi-store management
- Product configuration automation

